258
00:13:54,541 --> 00:13:56,976
PAIGE MICHAELCHUK. IT'S VERY NICE TO MEET YOU.

259
00:13:57,010 --> 00:13:59,412
I'VE HEARD SO MUCH ABOUT YOU.

260
00:14:02,615 --> 00:14:04,184
SMOOTH, MICHAELCHUK.

261
00:14:04,217 --> 00:14:06,519
BET YOU'RE ON THE NEXT FLIGHT TO HOLLYWOOD.

262
00:14:06,553 --> 00:14:08,521
HON, I'D RETHINK THE EYELINER.

263
00:14:08,555 --> 00:14:11,491
YOU'RE LOOKING A LITTLE WASHED OUT.

264
00:14:15,562 --> 00:14:18,131
THERE'S NO DOUBT TOBY'S A BRIGHT KID,

265
00:14:18,164 --> 00:14:18,998
BUT AH, HE HAS TROUBLE WITH DETAILS,

266
00:14:19,032 --> 00:14:20,533
