269
00:14:26,506 --> 00:14:28,241
FOR EXAMPLE, IN MEDIA IMMERSION,

270
00:14:28,274 --> 00:14:29,642
TOBY COULD BE AT THE TOP OF HIS CLASS

271
00:14:29,676 --> 00:14:31,611
IF HE JUST APPLIED HIMSELF.

272
00:14:31,644 --> 00:14:34,147
APPLY IS SUCH A RELATIVE TERM.

273
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:38,351
