373
00:20:06,579 --> 00:20:09,715
I'M A LITTLE OUTSPOKEN. IT RUNS IN THE FAMILY.

374
00:20:09,749 --> 00:20:12,685
MAYBE IT'S CONTAGIOUS. DID YOU HEAR MY BROTHER?

375
00:20:12,718 --> 00:20:13,819
LOOKS LIKE GARBAGE.

376
00:20:13,853 --> 00:20:16,322
SMELLS LIKE GARBAGE...

377
00:20:22,028 --> 00:20:23,729
IT WASN'T GARBAGE.

378
00:20:25,898 --> 00:20:26,699
THANKS.

379
00:20:36,509 --> 00:20:41,614
TOBY? CAN I SPEAK WITH YOU FOR A MINUTE? LISTEN, YESTERDAY-

380
00:20:41,647 --> 00:20:44,684
