381
00:20:44,717 --> 00:20:49,956
TOBY, IT WASN'T YOUR FAULT. ARE THEY ALWAYS LIKE THAT?

382
00:20:49,989 --> 00:20:53,960
ONLY WHEN THEY'RE TOGETHER. ACTUALLY, MR. SIMPSON,

383
00:20:53,993 --> 00:20:57,463
YESTERDAY WAS GOOD. IT CLEARED A LOT OF AIR.

384
00:20:57,496 --> 00:21:01,634
I'M GLAD. OH, LISTEN, BEFORE I FORGET,

385
00:21:03,436 --> 00:21:06,305
NEXT TIME YOU WANT TO FORGE MY SIGNATURE,

386
00:21:06,339 --> 00:21:08,608
